channel.title: FareWell
channel.description:
I Think my time has came, to "grow up" And actually live a life. (not saying i didn't have one before), its just i think i'm growing up, and i've become more and more in-active everyday, due to work and college, 4 days a week working 8 hours a day, and then 3 days in college, and then for rsps. just can't do it no-more, i'd put my life in front off rsps communitys/rsps. i've had a good couple off years here, and met some great people, and some not. :P i've learnt alot from moparscape, and some off the people on here, i'd like to wish you all the best in the future, goodluck with school/college, i hope you don't fuck up school like i did, its really not worth it, i'll still [i]maybe[/i] be active on a day or two when i'm free.
Peace guys. Respect.
- Pot up pls.
